<h1><%= @platform_name %> API Usage Alert</h1>

<p>The <%= @platform_name %> API has used <strong><%= number_with_delimiter(@operations_today) %></strong> of <strong><%= number_with_delimiter(@limit) %></strong> daily operations (<%= @percentage %>%).</p>

<p>Remaining today: <strong><%= number_with_delimiter(@remaining) %></strong> operations.</p>

<p>If usage regularly approaches this limit, consider applying for a higher access tier with the platform or revisit the daily limit configured in <code>AdPlatforms::ApiUsageTracker::LIMITS</code>.</p>

<p>
  Thanks,<br>
  The mbuzz Team
</p>
